data.description: Room for all in this oversized tri-level in a highly sought after Norton Shores Neighborhood.  Just a  short distance the beaches of Lake Michigan, schools shopping and more! 5 bedrooms 3 full baths, full fenced back yard with sauna and inground pool. Home is being sold as is, where is, and will be ready for immediate occupancy. Bring your ideas and talent to make this home your own!  Great potential for the investor as well!
